AiSummaryContaineruniface_104mzj1727955704907.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mzj1727955704907.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mzj1727955704907.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mzj1727955704907\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Sets the maximum size of table names in the database. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mzj1727955704907__section_wf4_y35_xcc\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">Mnemonic</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">_PARAMS = table name size =\n\t\t\t\t\t</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var></p>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">Mnemonic</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">_PARAMS = tblnmsize =\n\t\t\t\t\t</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mzj1727955704907__topic_d31512e1_d31513e1_d31514e1_d31515e1_d31516e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1229760e72\">Arguments </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mzj1727955704907__p_d48107e1_d48108e1_d48109e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>—maximum number of\n\t\t\t\tcharacters allowed for table names.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mzj1727955704907__topic_d31517e1_d31518e1_d31519e1_d31520e1_d31521e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1229760e83\">Use </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"mzj1727955704907__table_iqy_tj5_xcc\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/><col style=\"width:33.33333333333333%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"mzj1727955704907__table_iqy_tj5_xcc__entry__1\">Applies to</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"mzj1727955704907__table_iqy_tj5_xcc__entry__2\">Mnemonic</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"mzj1727955704907__table_iqy_tj5_xcc__entry__3\">Connector Syntax</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"mzj1727955704907__table_iqy_tj5_xcc__entry__1\">Informix connector</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"mzj1727955704907__table_iqy_tj5_xcc__entry__2\">INF</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"mzj1727955704907__table_iqy_tj5_xcc__entry__3\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$INF_PARAMS</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mzj1727955704907__topic_d31527e1_d31528e1_d31529e1_d31530e1_d31531e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1229760e132\">Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Use the <code class=\"ph codeph\">table name size</code> option to specify the maximum size, in number of\n\t\t\t\tbytes, allowed for table names. </p>\n<div class=\"p\">When specified, the connector truncates table names to the specified size. The\n\t\t\t\tminimum size is <code class=\"ph codeph\">18</code> bytes and the maximum size is\n\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">128</code> bytes.<div class=\"div\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"mzj1727955704907__pre_e5z_j35_xcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">USYS$Mnemonic_PARAMS = table name size =  32</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8421325\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8421325\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "table name size Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 04, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Sets the maximum size of table names in the database. USYS$ Mnemonic _PARAMS = table name size = Number USYS$ Mnemonic _PARAMS = tblnmsize = Number Arguments Number —maximum number of characters allowed for table names. Use Applies to Mnemonic Connector Syntax Informix connector INF USYS$INF_PARAMS Description Use the table name size option to specify the maximum size, in number of bytes, allowed for table names. When specified, the connector truncates table names to the specified size. The minimum size is 18 bytes and the maximum size is 128 bytes. USYS$Mnemonic_PARAMS = table name size = 32 Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}